Need(Streaming of Need)
====================================
Needs are the objects that are necessary for survival of life at any given time and situation. In Other words once need make their life smooth.
Is it?...it may or may not be...
Once need not only for smooth of life but also bother of life too. It depends up on once understanding/observation only that can makes their need best fit for their life.

***Every step of life observation/understanding takes the lead for life***
It is very need to understand once need for smooth journey of their life.
Following example clarify more better.

let us one trek on a mountain.
One have to pack their needs for trekking. If one understand there will be cold on height, one will take hot cloth. If One understand it may be rain on trek, one take umbrella, if one understand there are many small hotel for launch on the path of trek, one could not take much food.One understand single shoo is not enough for journey, one take a extra shoo. If one understand they have to stay on hill in night, they can pack tent, stick for balance...so on...

It can be observe/understand, if the tracker understanding is poor, they can take some more material or some less material.

A single extra need bother for their trekking because they have to trek/lift with extra needs.
If A single necessary needs they left, it may mood off the hole journey.

***Need best fit for smooth life***
